front.gametext: Deploy on table. Once during your deploy phase, you may deploy a non-Interrupt card with 'door' in title from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle. At Endor sites where you have a scout, Rebel scouts are power -1 and forfeit -3. (Immune to Alter.)

pulls: A non-Interrupt card with door in its title
